data.title: Today’s famous birthdays list for October 26, 2022 includes celebrities Keith Urban, Seth MacFarlane
data.meta_description: Celebrities Keith Urban and Seth MacFarlane share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of famous people with birthdays on October 26, 2022 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:
Birthday wishes go out to Keith Urban, Seth MacFarlane and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on October 26th and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

Top celebrity birthdays on October 26, 2022

TV host Pat Sajak turns 76

Fun fact: Has appeared as a celebrity contestant on ‘Jeopardy!’

Musician Bootsy Collins turns 71

Fun fact: Originally from Cincinnati, Ohio

Actor James Pickens Jr. turns 70

Fun fact: Once appeared in an episode of ‘Yellowstone’ as a cowboy

Actress Rita Wilson turns 66

Fun fact: Like her husband, she also appeared in an episode of ‘1883′

Actor Dylan McDermott turns 61

Fun fact: Was once engaged to actress Maggie Q

Singer Natalie Merchant turns 59

Fun fact: Has also directed several documentaries

Singer Keith Urban turns 55

Fun fact: Urban was born in New Zealand

Actor Seth MacFarlane turns 49

Fun fact: Hosted the Oscars in 2013

Check out more interesting facts about Seth MacFarlane.

Actor Jon Heder turns 45

Fun fact: Once appeared in an episode of ‘How I Met Your Mother’ as a character named Narshall

Moffett (“Chicago Med”) is 68. Actor Patrick Breen (“Madam Secretary”) is 62. Actor Cary Elwes is 60. Actor Steve Valentine (“Crossing Jordan”) is 56. Actor Tom Cavanagh (“The Flash,” ″Ed”) is 54. Actor Rosemarie DeWitt (“The United States of Tara”) is 51. Actor Anthony Rapp (“Rent”) is 51. TV host Paula Faris (“The View”) is 47. Actor Florence Kasumba (“Black Panther”) is 46. Singer Mark Barry of BBMak is 44. Actor Folake Olowofoyeku (“Bob Hearts Abishola”) is 39. Rapper Schoolboy Q is 36. Actor Beulah Koale (”Hawaii Five-0″) is 31.
